saunters in with quite the feast.\n\nThis is a VR Animation of Spice and Wolf: Spring Log, sequel to the original Spice and Wolf VR animation.\nThe game has a 30 minute story and a game mode where you can watch part of the anime alongside its characters in the style of Japanese paper street theater.\nA peaceful life in the bathhouse with wolfgirls awaits.\n", "short_description": "The team behind the original series has gotten together to bring you into the world of Spice and Wolf again for a second installment of VR animation! \nAnimation has evolved from \"watching\" to \"experiencing.\""}, {"images": {"nodes": [{"file_name": "Oculus_Icon_mobile.png", "id": "1064913614018317", "image_type": "APP_IMG_ICON", "uri": "https://scontent.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/75375083_1064913617351650_8414523728123351065_n.png?_nc_cat=109&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=GJ-DHqvkcocQ7kNvgFVYd3J&_nc_ht=scontent.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYDJbA2phBZ6tYrBda0Hn4v9SK-SpeLjcf5Uds55nTsA1A&oe=66EC00D1"}, {"file_name": "Oculus_Landscape.png", "id": "888092388709773", "image_type": "APP_IMG_COVER_LANDSCAPE", "uri": "https://scontent.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/75221313_888092392043106_3388339122400482554_n.png?_nc_cat=100&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=JVd8enVxtzgQ7kNvgF5GrXT&_nc_ht=scontent.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYAEKspuialcB_hvfV6R6Ibuf26DahyZUSVsYh5hnpz6mQ&oe=66EC2408"}, {"file_name": "Oculus_VRLandscape.png", "id": "723262801706006", "image_type": "APP_IMG_SMALL_LANDSCAPE", "uri": "https://scontent.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/38982668_723262805039339_6616665206780105350_n.png?_nc_cat=111&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=S3l1wbDihHIQ7kNvgEHxAq5&_nc_ht=scontent.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYA70f-URKrrttSZw75YNrDYgdMSsfu2tnuf80NirFdA5g&oe=66EBFB25"}, {"file_name": "Oculus_Hero.png", "id": "714465152559029", "image_type": "APP_IMG_HERO", "uri": "https://scontent.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/75367592_714465155892362_8370308211571510202_n.png?_nc_cat=102&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=_jDPb-ZGqjoQ7kNvgGfGycL&_nc_h